"```sql\nSELECT DISTINCT client.client_id\nFROM trans\nJOIN card ON trans.account_id = card.account_id\nJOIN disp ON card.disp_id = disp.disp_id\nJOIN client ON disp.client_id = client.client_id\nWHERE trans.type = 'VYDAJ' \nAND trans.amount < (\n    SELECT AVG(trans.amount)\n    FROM trans\n    WHERE trans.date BETWEEN '1998-01-01' AND '1998-12-31'\n    AND trans.type = 'VYDAJ'\n)\nAND trans.date BETWEEN '1998-01-01' AND '1998-12-31';\n``` \n\nThis SQL query selects the distinct client identification numbers of account holders who have made credit card withdrawals (indicated by the operation 'VYBER KARTOU') with amounts less than the average transaction amount for the year 1998. The subquery calculates the average transaction amount for the specified year, and the main query filters transactions based on that average."